- Add the ramAccounting variable initialization at the start of the method.
- Change getConsumer method to accept SelectSymbol and ramAccounting, and adapt the call accordingly.
- Keep the original context lines unchanged and keep at least 3 lines of context before and after the patch.

I will now generate a patch that respects the old version's context and adds the new logic accordingly.

